p: Proteome Discoverer 2.1 (Thermo Fisher Scientific, MA, USA) software was used to convert the original map files (.raw files) generated by Q Exactive into.mgf files, which were submitted to the MASCOT2.6 server for database retrieval through the built-in tools of the software. The database used was Uniprot_HomoSapiens_20386_20180905. The reliable protein screening criterion was peptide FDR ≤ 0.01.
